This is my first iceskate map i ever made! Its just a little arena with 2 ramps out of it. From those ramps u can jump to another place with a shotgun. If u fail u loose 10hp!! -------------------------------------------------- Special Thanks: GraffitiFlow (Skybox) Hellraisedsurfer Sangre Nueva mapping-tutorials.de surf-velocity.com mapjunkies.com -------------------------------------------------- Skate Instructions: It's Simple
  • If u walk, just stand still a moment and u fly up,
  • now begin to strafe from right to left and again and again and again.... like bunnyhop without the jump
Thats it ;) --------------------------------------------------
